title: Deep Learning For Gophers
abstract: The software has not eaten the world yet, but infact has changed the way it was before. That software has given us, the human a new superpower which is the power of artificial neural networks. The goal of those networks is to help us answer the question : “Given X, predict Y with Z% accuracy”. This is where Deep Learning comes into picture. Let’s build a basic building block of deep learning : neural network.
